      "writtenOn": "2020-08-14T05:09:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Not sure if I understand it correctly or not, but I want to revisit the \"stop condition\" here.\n\nLet\u0027s say you want to get the blamelist of the first build of a builder, because there is no \"previous build\", so len(builds) always be 0, so it will return every commit?",
      "revId": "8c2149922aab81bb573bcf44b363d878ace373e1",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
